# List Webhooks | Guide - Overview
created: 2024-03-20, last updated: 2026-03-07, [Read more](https://exciting-quinoa-nsuar.apidocumentation.com/guide/webhooks/list-webhooks)

The List Webhooks endpoint retrieves all webhook configurations associated with your authenticated application.
This endpoint provides comprehensive information about each webhook, including delivery statistics and current status, enabling effective webhook management and monitoring.
...
- **URL**:
```
/api/v0/webhooks
```
- **Method**:
```
